description: This skill makes Alexa give some funny comebacks from Al bundy. The source is twitter https://twitter.com/albundyquotes. Basically if you ask alexa something that is like how are, how do you feel she will answer with something funny taken from that wall (first 25 tweets).
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask bundy smarts to say something
name: Al Bundy smarts
shortDescription: Alexa will have Al Bundy's attitude and try to cheer you up with some funny quotes from Al Bundy
